  "markup": "\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionWrap faqs\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat is LaserTherapyU.org?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nLaserTherapyU.org is the web\u0026rsquo;s ultimate resource for research, webinars, abstracts, protocols and more on low-level laser technology and laser therapy. Geared to both professionals and consumers alike, LaserTherapyU.org houses the most up-to-date research found worldwide on the benefits of laser therapy.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHow much does it cost?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nWe offer 2 different ways to purchase the content you see on LaserTherapyU.org, subscription and ala carte.\n\u003Cul\u003E\n    \u003Cli\u003ESubscription: For medical professionals, there are two different subscription levels; 3-month and 12-month subscriptions. In addition to having access to unlimited content for one low price, there are additional benefits to being a subscriber, \u003Ca href=\u0022/subscriptions\u0022\u003Eclick here\u003C/a\u003E to learn more.\u003C/li\u003E\n    \u003Cli\u003EA La Carte: For those that just want to purchase content on a one-by-one basis, we offer individual pricing for each piece of content.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIf I\u0432\u0402\u2122m a subscriber, is there a limit to the amount of information I can download?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nNo \u0026ndash; there is no limit to the content you can access and download, you just have to do it while your subscription is active.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat forms of payment do you accept?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nWe accept all major credit cards: Visa, Mastercard, Discover and American Express.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDo I need to register before I can make a purchase?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nYes, you must \u003Ca href=\u0022/account/registration\u0022\u003Eregister\u003C/a\u003E with LaserTherapyU.org before you make a purchase.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHelp \u0432\u0402\u201C I downloaded a protocol, but I don\u0432\u0402\u2122t remember where I saved it on my computer! What can I do?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nYou will be able to access all your previous purchases in your \u003Ca href=\u0022/account/my-profile\u0022\u003Euser profile page\u003C/a\u003E.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCan I view my order history?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nYes, in the \u003Ca href=\u0022/account/my-profile\u0022\u003Euser profile page\u003C/a\u003E, you can view all of your previous purchases.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tI just tried to purchase a webinar, but the message indicated that I wasn\u0432\u0402\u2122t authorized to purchase. Why is that?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nLaserTherapyU.org takes extra steps to ensure the information you are looking for is geared to your level of laser knowledge and familiarity. Certain types of information aren\u0026rsquo;t available for consumers to purchase, simply because the information is more technical in nature and geared towards healthcare professionals.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionPanel\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionHeader\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionToggle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Accordion Toggle\u0022 src=\u0022/presentation/laserU/images/accordionToggle_Plus.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionTitle\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhy is there a charge to LaserTherapyU.org?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cdiv class=\u0022accordionContent\u0022 style=\u0022display: none;\u0022\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022theBlue\u0022\u003EA:\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cbr /\u003E\nMuch of LaseTherapyU.org is free for anyone to access to learn more about laser therapy and the benefits it provides.\u0026nbsp; However, nominal fees are charged to cover the cost of the provision of the service, as well as to support the ongoing development of new protocols, webinars and other high-quality content.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E\n    \n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003C/div\u003E"
}]]></Value>
    </content>
